TypeSignature.Value: .class public auto ansi beforefieldinit Source extends DocumentFormat.OpenXml.OpenXmlCompositeElement

summary.para: Source.
This class is available in Office 2007 or above.
When the object is serialized out as xml, it's qualified name is b:Source.

remarks.format:
## Remarks [!INCLUDE[openxmlnoticeiso](~/includes/openxmlnoticeiso.md)]
**Source (Source)**
This element specifies the bibliography entry for a source or reference work. [*Example*:
```xml <b:Source> … <b:NumberVolumes>10</b:NumberVolumes> <b:Comments> Comments</b:Comments> </b:Source> ```
*end example*]
